<title>USA: PHLX to list Legg Mason, NGC options.</title>
<headline>PHLX to list Legg Mason, NGC options.</headline>
<dateline>CHICAGO 1997-04-25</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Philadelphia Stock Exchange (PHLX) said it will list options on Legg Mason Inc and NGC Corp shares on May 1.</p>
<p>Legg Mason options will have initial strike prices of 40, 45 and 50, with expirations in May, June, August and November.</p>
<p>NGC options will have strikes of 15, 17-1/2 and 20 with expirations in May, June, September and December.</p>
<p>Spear, Leeds &amp; Kellogg will be the specialist for both options, which will have position limits of 4,500 contracts each.</p>
<p>- Chicago Derivatives Desk ((312-408-8750))</p>
<p>E-mail: derivatives@reuters.com</p>
